ORIGINAL WORK & MODIFICATIONS
================================================================================

The following files were created or substantially modified by this project and
are provided under the same Apache License, Version 2.0:

  - xtensa_mtk_le.slaspec
        New standalone spec that builds the stock Xtensa base ISA, removes the
        @include directives for "flix.sinc" and "cust.sinc", and instead
        @includes "xtensa-mtk.sinc".

  - xtensa-mtk.sinc
        New file authored specifically for this project. It adds length-correct,
        opaque (CALLOTHER) constructors for MediaTek Connac2 "Neptune" custom-TIE
        opcodes (op0 in {E,F,4}, QRST CUST0/CUST1, and the reserved RST/ST3/BI1
        lanes). It functionally replaces Ghidra's flix.sinc and cust.sinc for
        the purposes of this processor module.

