PROPRIETARY CONTENT DISCLAIMER
================================================================================

This repository does NOT contain, redistribute, or reference any of the
following:

  - MediaTek proprietary source code, firmware blobs, or cryptographic keys
  - Tensilica / Cadence proprietary TIE or processor configuration files
  - Any confidential documentation licensed by MediaTek or its affiliates

The custom opcodes are implemented as opaque intrinsics (CALLOTHER) precisely
because the underlying vendor configuration is not public. All opcode
encodings and semantics represented here were derived through independent
reverse engineering of public firmware images and ISA behavior, and are
expressed as abstract placeholders where the exact functional semantics are
not publicly documented.